Subject: Re: [T2] Riddle me this, Batman - Gas in my oil??? 77 Westy

On 8/25/2012 3:32 PM, Courtney Hook wrote:
> odd, so smelled it, and it smells of gas. Leaky injector?? I can't figure how
> this would happen on a stock 2.0L F.I. engine? Never happened to me before,

Injectors don't like to sit - they like to be used.  I'd pull the 
injectors off of the intake manifolds and power up the pump by sticking 
a screwdriver into the intake (with the air filter removed).  See if any 
of the injectors are leaking (including the cold-start injector).
